== Korintkarank Pauluchem Poilem Potr ==
'''First Epistle to the Corinthians'''


==== Korintkarank Pauluchem Poilem Potr ====

Gresia desant, Korint xarant Judevancho ek zomo aslo, ani hem xar moddon poddlolea eka Grik xaracher bandlolem.  Dhormdutanchea kallar girestkaien ani veapar-dhondean tem borench voir aslem, punn noitik jivitant sarkem mhellem zal’lem.

Aple dusre dhormporgottneche bhonvddent,  Paulun don vorsam Korintant xikovnn dili, poilem devsthanant Judevank, ani upant, Titus Justus hachea ghora, videxiank.  Aten xarant,  Kristanv dhorma vixim, unch totvamnim bhorloli tannem kel’li boli onupeogi zal’li dekhun, Korint xarant Paulun sadea ulovpachi vat dhorli.  Devan adim bhasail’lem toxem (DI 8/9 ani her-kodden polle), tannem zaitea videxianchem mon bodol’lem, punn Judevanche dusman’kaiek lagun taka khub soschem poddlem.

Korintkarank boroil’lim Pauluchim don potram amkam pavleant, punn tanche bhair,  Paulun  Korintkarank anink ek potr boroil’lem-xem dista. Efezache povitr-sobheche kai vangddi Korintantle povitrsobhek bhett korunk ail’le, te bhettecho foll koso,  Paulun Korintkarank hem potr boroilem.

Paulu nigtoch Antiokie thaun portun ieun, tisre bhonvdder aslo tedna Korintantle povitr-sobhent duspott zalear mhonn hea niropiam udexim taka kollun ailem.  Novxisamnim aplea atmik gurunk thodde prosn ghal’le ani te-I tachea nirnnoiak vo zobabak ravtale.  Duspott zal’li ti nittaier ghalunk ani tanchea vicharank zobab diunk Paulun hem xastrik potr boroilem.

Tannem suttave kele te prosn he : chuku vinnem Kristi jivit,  logn ani ankvarponn,  Somiachem Jevonn, Povitr Atmean dil’lea vorgunnancho favo to upeog, nitixallamnim khottle, kuddea-devank bhettoil’lem khan-jevonn.

Hea potrachea 16vea ovesvorantlea 5-8 vollim pormannem, Pon’nasavea Disachea Utsova adim, Efez xarant, chodd korun 57 vea vorsache survatek, tannem hem potr boroilem-xem dista.

